&lt;p>Have you ever seen a person &lt;br>
Who hires someone else to love &lt;br>
his/her spouse and children?&lt;/p>
&lt;p>It is unthinkable, &lt;br>
we call that person &lt;br>
out of his mind.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Have you seen any person &lt;br>
Who hires someone to write poetry and sing &lt;br>
for his/her loved one or for his/her spouse?&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>